---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import FloatingPaths from '../../components/FloatingPaths.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="SEO Services Kansas City | Dominion.Digital"
  description="SEO services for Kansas City businesses and national brands. Technical SEO, on-page optimization, local SEO, and link building that drives organic growth and leads."
  canonicalUrl="https://dominion.digital/internet-marketing/seo"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    [
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 1,
            "name": "Home",
            "item": "https://dominion.digital"
          },
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 2,
            "name": "Internet Marketing",
            "item": "https://dominion.digital/internet-marketing"
          },
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 3,
            "name": "SEO Services",
            "item": "https://dominion.digital/internet-marketing/seo"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Service",
        "@id": "https://dominion.digital/internet-marketing/seo#service",
        "name": "SEO Services",
        "serviceType": "Search Engine Optimization",
        "provider": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "@id": "https://dominion.digital/#organization",
          "name": "Dominion.Digital"
        },
        "areaServed": {
          "@type": "City",
          "name": "Kansas City",
          "addressRegion": "MO"
        },
        "url": "https://dominion.digital/internet-marketing/seo"
      },
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long does SEO take to produce results?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Dominion.Digital moves rankings in weeks. Most clients see measurable movement within the first 30 to 60 days. The exact timeline depends on your starting position and keyword competition, but early wins show up fast and the reporting makes them visible from day one."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Do I need to keep doing SEO once I reach page one?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Yes. Rankings are held by whoever is doing the most consistent work. A competitor who starts investing in SEO after you can close the gap if you stop. The businesses that hold top positions long term treat SEO as an ongoing system."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Does SEO include Google Business Profile?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Yes. Local SEO and Google Business Profile optimization are included in every SEO engagement. Map pack rankings are often more valuable than organic rankings for local service businesses in Kansas City, and both are covered."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
    </script>
  </Fragment>

  <Nav />

  <main>

    <!-- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section
      class="relative"
      style="padding-top: clamp(9rem, 18vw, 14rem); padding-bottom: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem);"
      aria-label="SEO Services hero"
    >
      <FloatingPaths />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(200,81,26,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%); z-index: 0;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="container relative" style="z-index: 1;">

        <!-- Breadcrumb -->
        <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 reveal" style="color: #8a8880;">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors duration-200">Home</a>
          <span style="margin: 0 0.5rem; color: rgba(240,235,225,0.25);">/</span>
          <a href="/internet-marketing" class="hover:text-text transition-colors duration-200">Internet Marketing</a>
          <span style="margin: 0 0.5rem; color: rgba(240,235,225,0.25);">/</span>
          SEO Services
        </p>

        <h1
          class="font-display font-extrabold text-text tracking-tighter leading-none reveal"
          style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6.5vw, 6.5rem); max-width: 18ch; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
        >
          SEO Services That Get Kansas City Businesses to Page One
        </h1>

        <p class="font-body text-text-muted reveal" style="font-size: 1.125rem; max-width: 52ch; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
          Rankings don't come from one trick. They come from technical SEO, on-page optimization, link building, and content: done consistently. Dominion.Digital handles all of it and shows you the numbers.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 reveal">
          <button
            type="button"
            data-open-contact
            class="btn-cta inline-flex items-center font-label font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-text bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover active:scale-[0.97] transition-all duration-200"
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;"
          >
            Get My Free SEO Audit
          </button>
          <a
            href="/internet-marketing/geo"
            class="inline-flex items-center font-label font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200"
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.25); border-radius: 9999px;"
            id="hero-ghost-secondary"
          >
            See GEO Services
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ─── OPENING / PUNCHLINE ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Pattern A: 3fr/2fr split — narrative left, punchline card right -->
    <section
      style="padding-top: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); padding-bottom: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem);"
      aria-labelledby="opening-punchline"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] items-start gap-16 md:gap-24" id="opening-block">

          <!-- Left: narrative -->
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5" style="color: #8a8880;">
              Internet Marketing / SEO
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-6" style="max-width: 60ch;">
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
                When a potential customer searches for what you offer in Kansas City, one of three things happens: they find you, they find a competitor, or they find no one useful and go back to searching. The first option is the only one that pays.
              </p>
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
                Internet marketing service providers talk about SEO constantly. Few build it the right way. Dominion.Digital's approach covers the full picture: the technical health of your site, the strength of your on-page content, and the authority built through links from other trusted sources. All three have to work together. Fixing only one leaves real ranking potential on the table.
              </p>
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
                Every engagement starts with an audit that surfaces exactly where rankings are being lost. From there, the work is systematic: fix what's broken, build what's missing, and track what's moving month over month.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: punchline card -->
          <div class="reveal" id="punchline-card" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <div style="border: 1px solid rgba(200,81,26,0.25); padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
              <div aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, rgba(200,81,26,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
              <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6" style="color: #8a8880;">
                The Principle
              </p>
              <p
                class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-text"
                id="opening-punchline"
                style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem); line-height: 1.2;"
              >
                Your rankings move in weeks. Page one means people find you every day without you paying for each click.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ─── WHAT'S INCLUDED ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Pattern A flipped: 2fr/3fr — pills left, bento list right, surface bg -->
    <section
      style="padding-top: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); padding-bottom: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); background: #161614;"
      aria-labelledby="includes-heading"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] items-start gap-16 md:gap-24" id="includes-block">

          <!-- Left: label + pills + trust anchor -->
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5" style="color: #8a8880;">
              What's Included
            </p>
            <h2
              id="includes-heading"
              class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-text"
              style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1;"
            >
              Rankings That<br />Compound Over Time.
            </h2>

            <!-- Pill cluster: Rapid Fire Benefits -->
            <div class="stagger" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;" aria-label="SEO capabilities">
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">Technical SEO Audit</span>
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">On-Page Optimization</span>
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">Local SEO &amp; Map Pack</span>
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">Link Building</span>
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">Monthly Rank Reporting</span>
              <span class="font-label tracking-widest uppercase text-text" style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.15); border-radius: 9999px;">E-E-A-T Content Strategy</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Trust anchor -->
            <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,81,26,0.2); padding-top: 1.5rem;">
              <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: #c8511a; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                The Website Guarantee
              </p>
              <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Any SEO engagement that includes a web component is covered by the Website Guarantee. If you're not satisfied before launch, you get every dollar back.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Bento Checkmarks — Scope / Inclusion List -->
          <div>
            <ul class="stagger space-y-3" aria-label="What SEO includes">

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Technical SEO audit</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Crawl errors, site speed, Core Web Vitals, indexability, and mobile usability reviewed and remediated</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">On-page optimization</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Title tags, meta descriptions, header structure, internal linking, and keyword targeting across every target page</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Local SEO</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Google Business Profile optimization, map pack targeting, local citation building, and review management integration</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Link building</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Outreach-based backlinks from relevant, authoritative sources that build domain authority over time</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Content strategy</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Keyword research mapped to your services, with a content plan built to grow topical authority on Google and in AI search</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: rgba(13,13,11,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.07);">
                <svg style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem; color: #c8511a;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Monthly reporting</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Ranking movement, organic traffic, and lead attribution tracked and delivered every month</p>
                </div>
              </li>

            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ─── WHY IT MATTERS ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Pattern A: stat callout left, narrative right -->
    <section
      style="padding-top: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); padding-bottom: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem);"
      aria-labelledby="matters-heading"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] items-start gap-16 md:gap-24" id="matters-block">

          <!-- Left: stat callout -->
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5" style="color: #8a8880;">
              The Case for Organic
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-display font-bold tracking-tighter text-accent"
              style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
            >
              Page 1.
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1rem; max-width: 28ch; line-height: 1.5;">
              The majority of clicks go to the first page of results. Businesses not on page one are invisible to most of their market.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: narrative -->
          <div>
            <h2
              id="matters-heading"
              class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-text"
              style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1;"
            >
              Organic Rankings Pay Back for Years.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6" style="max-width: 58ch;">
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
                A business ranking on page one for its primary keywords in Kansas City generates leads every day without paying for each click. That compounds. A page ranked this quarter can still be delivering qualified traffic a year from now without additional spend.
              </p>
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
                Google's E-E-A-T framework rewards sites that demonstrate real depth: experience, expertise, authoritativeness, and trust. Thin pages and one-off blog posts don't build that. A sustained content and link strategy does. The businesses holding top positions in Kansas City search are building consistently, and they get harder to displace every month.
              </p>
              <p class="font-body leading-relaxed text-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 500;">
                The cost of waiting is measured in leads that went to whoever ranked first.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ─── HOW WE APPROACH IT ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Pattern E: Sticky sidecar, surface bg -->
    <section
      style="padding-top: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); padding-bottom: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem); background: #161614;"
      aria-labelledby="process-heading"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] items-start gap-16 md:gap-24" id="process-block">

          <!-- Left: sticky label + heading -->
          <div class="md:sticky" style="top: 6rem;">
            <p class="font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5" style="color: #8a8880;">
              The Process
            </p>
            <h2
              id="process-heading"
              class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-text"
              style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.1;"
            >
              Audit First. Build What Ranks.
            </h2>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 1rem; max-width: 32ch; line-height: 1.6;">
              Every Dominion.Digital SEO engagement starts with a full audit. What's broken technically, what keywords you're close to ranking for, where competitors are outranking you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: process steps -->
          <div>
            <ul class="stagger" aria-label="SEO process steps">

              <li class="py-6" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08);">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.25rem;">
                  <span class="font-label font-bold" style="color: #c8511a; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">01</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">Full audit</p>
                    <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Technical health, keyword gap analysis, competitor ranking review, and site structure evaluated before any work begins. You see the full picture on day one.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="py-6" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08);">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.25rem;">
                  <span class="font-label font-bold" style="color: #c8511a; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">02</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">Technical remediation</p>
                    <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Crawl errors, Core Web Vitals, indexability issues, and mobile usability problems fixed first. A clean technical foundation is what everything else builds on.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="py-6" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08);">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.25rem;">
                  <span class="font-label font-bold" style="color: #c8511a; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">03</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">On-page optimization</p>
                    <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Title tags, headers, internal links, and keyword targeting updated across every service page. Google Business Profile and map pack optimization runs in parallel.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="py-6" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08);">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.25rem;">
                  <span class="font-label font-bold" style="color: #c8511a; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">04</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">Link building and content</p>
                    <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Outreach-based backlinks and keyword-targeted content run together once the foundation is stable. Both are built to support traditional rankings and AI search citation at the same time.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="py-6" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,235,225,0.08);">
